data.text:
Prince Albert Of Belgium - Born June 6, 1934; brother of King Baudouin of Belgium, he is the Heir Presumptive. His formal title is Prince of Liege. Prince Albert Of Liege - who represented his brother, King Baudouin of Belgium at the Coronation, came to Perle "Call Me Madam" Mesta's fabulous party at Londonderry House, in London. December 17, 1952. (Photo by Camera Press).
